{"tid":2118991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.21周年 去年恐襲唔見人  今年重兵亂拉人","createTime":"2020-07-22T00:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T00:31:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48b2d60b41be2be6cae2c28c1678e21b68e37f65","tid":2118991,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:31:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200722/PSVPNDUNQ5QUZXSNHH7W7N4MBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FPSVPNDUNQ5QUZXSNHH7W7N4MBI%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=7afe842f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FPSVPNDUNQ5QUZXSNHH7W7N4MBI%2F&h=d2cb7199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200722/PSVPNDUNQ5QUZXSNHH7W7N4MBI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n7.21周年 去年恐襲唔見人 <br />\n今年重兵亂拉人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】7.21元朗鄉黑恐襲市民一周年，港人拒絕遺忘，號召到元朗港鐵站表態，去年「唔見人」兼遲大到、最終僅拘捕七名施襲者的防暴警察，一年後終大量現身，並以限聚令、非法集結及國安法之名打壓，截停搜查、發射胡椒球彈驅散、濫捕手無寸鐵市民甚至議員，共五人被捕，79人被票控。民主黨立法會議員林卓廷批評，警方至今仍「覺得自己啱晒」，又指一年前警方有昨日十分之一警力出現，7.21已不會發生。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：內部通訊揭元朗指揮官下令不理999<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gfW1ok3OoqoJClCSktFxy3ZZVW8=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CPP5MPZTXVCDLWQ4V6OBW3D7TY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgfW1ok3OoqoJClCSktFxy3ZZVW8%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCPP5MPZTXVCDLWQ4V6OBW3D7TY.jpg&h=d1f580bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批警察昨衝入Yoho Mall驅散及截查市民，與去年「無警時分」形成強烈對比。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BUkcBcucXXbXQG3q5KksKirnDiM=/652x466/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J64SPMWH4MMYE6T2OICSHOU65U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBUkcBcucXXbXQG3q5KksKirnDiM%3D%2F652x466%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ64SPMWH4MMYE6T2OICSHOU65U.gif&h=9191e778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有市民打扮成疑似7.21施襲兇徒，被警員截查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ywomSkGJ-lBP93-lgDz4rQL0cH8=/652x466/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/34EEXLXRY55YCBECLNZENLCUHI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FywomSkGJ-lBP93-lgDz4rQL0cH8%3D%2F652x466%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F34EEXLXRY55YCBECLNZENLCUHI.gif&h=317950b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵青區議員周偉雄因舉起「光復香港」紙牌，被指涉違國安法拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n昨日7.21一周年，有市民號召發起「721一周年：攬炒白色行動」，但警方煞有介事，昨午呼籲「市民不要參與未經批准的集結」，重申警方調查及部。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M1jj_zIabgoA3rUoqvZtZRIniZ4=/511x332/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XG5LMNRVQLXESOUC6ANJPGMKQA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM1jj_zIabgoA3rUoqvZtZRIniZ4%3D%2F511x332%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXG5LMNRVQLXESOUC6ANJPGMKQA.gif&h=323772ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名記者被警員截查，部份網媒及學生記者被發限聚令告票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ogJ806WxRlPvd5nqWPUIWtCD1TM=/511x332/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QKLCGTD35FI665XYYWKJNP4CSQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FogJ806WxRlPvd5nqWPUIWtCD1TM%3D%2F511x332%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQKLCGTD35FI665XYYWKJNP4CSQ.gif&h=eab33a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名市民在商場內高舉白紙抗議白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n票控記者 拘捕議員<br />\n<br />\n職工盟聯同元朗區議員麥業成在元朗發防疫物品，其間逾20名警員包圍街站，職工盟主席吳敏兒嘲諷與去年的「無警時分」形成極大對比，「當市民最需要警察嘅時候，去咗邊？」去年在元朗站內遇襲，事後反被建制派誣衊帶隊入元朗的林卓廷昨午在元朗站召開記者會，公開85名去年參與襲擊但未被拘捕疑兇大頭照，大批防暴警瞬即包圍，向他及同行職員等發多張限聚令告票，林斥警方濫用限聚令打壓民間聲音。<br />\n<br />\n及至傍晚，市民開始在Yoho Mall內聚集並叫口號，大批防暴警同樣提早到場並以限聚令驅散，又截查數十名年輕人再發限聚令告票，一名手持「追究7.21警。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n近百名在場記者同樣受警方阻撓採訪，除被查看記者證，更被無理搜身，又要除口罩拍攝容貌，部份網媒及學生記者被警方發限聚令告票。即使是議員一樣遭。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷：一定係心虛<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷晚上指警方昨日行為「一定係心虛啦」，形容昨派大量警力在元朗四處搜查市民是不知所謂，「如果一年前有呢度十分之一嘅警力、十分之一嘅認真程度，7.21已經唔會發生啦！」又指警方「覺得自己啱哂」，連向他發限聚令告票的警員也自以為大義凜然、理直氣壯。<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上透露，有79人在元朗因違反。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}